&lt;p&gt;We are looking to appoint a Speciality Doctor in Anaesthetics to join our forward thinking department at Diana Princess of Wales Hospital. Emergency, elective, intensive therapy and maternity services are provided within this unit. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Department provides general anaesthetic services for all the specialties within the Trust. These include General Surgery, Orthopaedics, ENT, Ophthalmology, Maxillofacial Surgery, Urology and Obstetrics and Gynaecology.&lt;/p&gt;
